{"article_id":"WB5Rc1HQ6HTzgIUA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"So we finally have actual election results from the state of New Hampshire .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"They are clear ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and they are authoritative","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and they are a little bit complicated .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"\" Hello , America. \"","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"\" We are here","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"to stay. \"","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"\" Our campaign is built for the long haul. \"","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"\" We ' re going to Nevada .","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"We ' re going to South Carolina .","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"We ' re going to win those states as well. \"","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"Bernie Sanders has won the state by a little bit .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"Two other candidates","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"who had quite a strong night -","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Pete Buttigieg and Amy Klobuchar .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"Not such a good night for Joe Biden or for Elizabeth Warren or for anybody else .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"\" New Hampshire. \"","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"\" New Hampshire. \"","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"\" New Hampshire. \"","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"\" We ' re here together. \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"\" New Hampshire. \"","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"\" You all up here in New Hampshire. \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"After the debacle in Iowa , national attention has focused even more intensely on New Hampshire as the first real clean test of political momentum in this race .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"\" People are still undecided. \"","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"\" Uh , Bernie. \"","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"\" Bernie Sanders , all the way. \"","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"\" Mayor Pete. \"","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"\" Amy Klobuchar. \"","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"\" Oh , Joe Biden. \"","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"\" I ' ll just probably decide Tuesday , five minutes","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"before I go in to vote. \"","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"New Hampshire is a classic swing state .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"\" Ronald Reagan is the winner in the state of New Hampshire. \"","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"\" Bill Clinton won it. \"","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"\" It ' s neck and neck. \"","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"\" New Hampshire goes to Obama. \"","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"In 2016 , Hillary Clinton prevailed over Donald Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"but by a tiny margin .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"It ' s a state","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that ' s very much in play for 2020 .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"\" Four more , Trump .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"Four more years ! \"","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"New Hampshire might gauge","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"whether a candidate is able to appeal to certain other constituencies","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"they will need in the general election .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"We have seen over the last week a real rivalry emerge between Bernie Sanders and Pete Buttigieg .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"\" Hot , fresh and vegan .","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Get your Bernie-on-a-stick. \"","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"New Hampshire is really home turf for Bernie Sanders .","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"He comes from right next door in Vermont .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"And he also drew strong support ,","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"as he did in 2016 ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"from younger voters and more liberal voters .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"\" Young voters want Bernie","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"because he ' s fighting for their future .","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"He ' s not fighting for his future .","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"He ' s in his future. \"","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"[ cheering ]","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Bernie Sanders came into New Hampshire","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"claiming momentum out of Iowa ,","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"based on his lead in the popular vote .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"\" Finally , the votes were counted in Iowa .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Took them a little while .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"We won the vote by 6,000 votes. \"","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"He has been somewhat more aggressive with his primary opponents here ...","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"\" We don ' t have a Super PAC. \" ...","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"talking about the difference between himself ...","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"\" We don ' t want billionaires ' money. \"","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"... and candidates in the race , like Pete Buttigieg ,","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"who take money from billionaires and other big donors .","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"\" We are running a campaign for working people ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"funded by working people .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"And that is why we are going to win here in New Hampshire and all over this country. \"","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"[ cheering ]","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"The biggest thing","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"this might mean for Bernie Sanders","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"is that he has clearly reasserted himself as the dominant leader on the left wing of the Democratic Party .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"And then there ' s Pete Buttigieg .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"\" Back in the Obama campaign , we called it ' no drama Obama , '","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"and I haven ' t come up with the right rhyme for Buttigieg. \"","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"[ cheering ]","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Pete Buttigieg has claimed , among the moderate candidates , a sense of momentum in New Hampshire","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"that other folks were not able to take .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"\" We can ' t risk dividing Americans further .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"The idea","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"that you ' ve either got to be for a revolution","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"or you got to be for the status quo","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"leaves most of us out. \"","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"His message here has been pretty similar to his message in Iowa ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"but really focused on the idea","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"that he ' s the candidate","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"who can win crossover support in the general election .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"\" We need a politics","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"that brings all of us in","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"because all of us need a new and better president. \"","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"After finishing at the top in both Iowa and New Hampshire ,","depth":3},{"id":96,"text":"Buttigieg now has a tremendous opportunity","depth":4},{"id":97,"text":"to put himself forward at the national level as the leader of moderate Democrats .","depth":4},{"id":98,"text":"Announcer :","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"\" Senator Amy Klobuchar ! \"","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"The word","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"that Amy Klobuchar supporters are using","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"to describe what happened here","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"is ' Klomentum. '","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"She came to New Hampshire after a fifth-place finish in Iowa","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"without a whole lot of wind in her sails .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"\" It ' s been funny suddenly seeing media come to all of our events. \"","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"[ laughter ]","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Things just turned around for her dramatically .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"If Klobuchar had not finished so strong in New Hampshire ,","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"it might have been the end of her campaign .","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"\" If you are tired of the extremes in our politics ,","depth":5},{"id":112,"text":"and you are tired of the noise and the nonsense ,","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"you have a home with me. \"","depth":4},{"id":114,"text":"She gets the chance","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"to fight onward to Nevada and South Carolina and Super Tuesday .","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"I would not make any plans","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"that are based on knowing a Democratic nominee","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"anytime soon .","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"Well , I am going to Las Vegas next ,","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"so I probably would have a chance","depth":6},{"id":121,"text":"to do that .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":243,"left":219,"right":242,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":219,"left":216,"right":218,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":216,"left":125,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":0,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":1,"right":123,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":215,"left":178,"right":214,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":143,"right":177,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":136,"right":142,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":136,"left":131,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":4,"right":130,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":126,"right":129,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":7,"right":128,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":128,"left":8,"right":127,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":135,"left":11,"right":134,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":133,"right":15,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":132,"right":14,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":132,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elab